**Aim of Feedback: Rolsa Technologies**

To determine how effective the prototype of the proposed solution is, and to assess how well it meets the client's and users’ needs, I will be creating separate questionnaires for two user groups: **technical** and **non-technical**. These surveys will focus on specific aspects of the Rolsa Technologies platform — such as booking, account functionality, accessibility, and clarity of energy-related information — rather than just general opinions.

---

## **Feedback Plan Overview**

| **Audience**                    | **Prototype Options**                                                                                                                                                                                                                  | **Prototype You Will Produce**                                                                                                                                                                                                  | **Questions to Ask About the Prototype**                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        | **Method of Gathering Feedback**                                                                                                                                                                                                       | **Who to Get Feedback From & Why**                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
| ------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Technical & Non-Technical Users | I considered multiple ways of presenting the Rolsa platform — including live walkthroughs or presentations. However, for this educational project, sending a link to the working prototype or a demonstration video is more practical. | Due to this being a prototype, I will provide a link to the deployed version of the site or a recorded walkthrough. I will also include screenshots of critical areas like the booking system, dashboard, and account settings. | - What is your name?<br>- Please rate your first impression of the website.<br>- Does the website give you a clear understanding of its purpose?<br>- What do you like least/most about the site?<br>- How would you describe the visual design?<br>- Is the layout intuitive and easy to navigate?<br>- Was it easy to find the booking or account buttons?<br>- What are your thoughts on the logo and navigation bar?<br>- How would you rate the homepage and its purpose?<br>- Did you interact with any buttons, and did they work?<br>- Is the animals/solutions section engaging?<br>- Is it useful to show opening times or energy system info upfront?<br>- Thoughts on having a map embedded on the about/contact page?<br>- Rate the EduVisit/Services page.<br>- Was the booking system simple?<br>- Did the login/signup work smoothly?<br>- Did you notice helpful prompts (e.g. "You must log in to book")?<br>- Once logged in, did you notice any personalisation (e.g. dashboard updates)?<br>- Can you see your bookings or rewards clearly on the user dashboard?<br>- Please rate the visual design of the main booking page.<br>- Was the database structure logical (technical only)?<br>- Did you notice efficient folder structure or naming conventions (technical only)?<br>- Any general feedback for improvement? | Microsoft Forms will be used to gather feedback. This allows for a mix of rating questions, long answer responses, and branching logic based on user type (technical or non-technical). Screenshots will also be included for clarity. | All testers will be my classmates. I will categorise them into technical and non-technical groups and ask them to choose their type before filling out the rest of the form. This will help segment the responses and gather feedback specific to each audience. |


